  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Begin as a skeleton, fight, gather resources, and craft armor/weapons to upgrade your bones.</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/320a658552a46a0c2d83c71fc08b89fd.poster.avif?t=1690996186\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/320a658552a46a0c2d83c71fc08b89fd.webm?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/320a658552a46a0c2d83c71fc08b89fd.mp4?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/1f9a1b85731dc598d37ee6a7d1cd8f64.avif?t=1690996186\" width=594 height=98 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The world of Skullborn is a <strong>persistent infinite procedurally generated</strong> universe that all players join.</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/c01d8c0881fd8dbb11f6a2b69f913a0b.poster.avif?t=1690996186\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/c01d8c0881fd8dbb11f6a2b69f913a0b.webm?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/c01d8c0881fd8dbb11f6a2b69f913a0b.mp4?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/26a521870ce1d13e2aed5d8623125e2e.avif?t=1690996186\" width=594 height=99 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >As you explore you will find other players and their buildings, villages, and other creations. As well as able to create your own base with your friends.</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/26087506c7a38382be168f4c8369b5bd.poster.avif?t=1690996186\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/26087506c7a38382be168f4c8369b5bd.webm?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/26087506c7a38382be168f4c8369b5bd.mp4?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You will also find player created dungeons with valuable loot!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/3e809b2a2774566273ccc189f6b8913e.poster.avif?t=1690996186\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/3e809b2a2774566273ccc189f6b8913e.webm?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841200/extras/3e809b2a2774566273ccc189f6b8913e.mp4?t=1690996186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infinite players, world, and possibilities. Become anything in Skullborn.</h2></strong>",
